snippet.title: Version 2.7 Trailer — "A New Venture on the Eighth Dawn" | Honkai: Star Rail
snippet.description:
Some will return, some will soon leave. The Dreamscape is embroiled with murk and uncertainty. To behold the path ahead, one must learn to retrospect.

English Voice:
"Shush" —Craig Lee Thomas
Fugue — Anya Floris
Sunday — Griffin Puatu
Herta — PJ Mattson
